-- Drake & Scull Will Announce Second Acquisition in Saudi Arabia in a Week
-- B y   A y e s h a   D a y a
-- 2010-11-09T07:24:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/drake-scull-will-announce-second-acquisition-in-saudi-arabia-in-a-week.html
Drake & Scull International PJSC will
announce a second acquisition in Saudi Arabia in a week, the
company’s chief executive officer said.  The engineering contractor for the real-estate industry’s
order book will exceed 4.9 billion dirhams by year-end and it
hopes to enter the Indian market next year, Khaldoun Tabari told
reporters in Dubai today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ayesha Daya in Dubai at 
